						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Rājarāja I. Year 23: A.D. 1008.</hi></p>						

						<p>Beginning lost and portions damaged. Seems to refer to an <hi rend="italic">iṟaiyili</hi> grant of land to the shrine of Veṇṇaikkūttāḍi-aruḷugiṉṟa Āḷvār (Krishṇa) in Tirunārāyaṇa Viṇṇagar of Nālūr, a <hi rend="italic">brahmadēya</hi> in Chēṟṟūrk-kūṟṟam, a subdivision of Kshatri[ya]śikhāmaṇi-vaḷanāḍu. Mentions that the assembly met at the big hall called Gaṇḍarādittaṉ.</p>						

						</summary>
